                           .toString());

                     userExpectedList.get(i).setTripNameActualPM(  
                           userActualList.get(j).getTripName());  
                     userExpectedList.get(i).setActFencePM(  
                           userActualList.get(j).getFenceName());

                           userActualList.get(j).getSwipeTime()  
                           .toString());

                  isPresent = true;  
                  userActualList.remove(j); // After updating swipe info  
                  // remove student from

               }

public static HashMap<String, Object> loadProperties(String propertyFile) {

    Enumeration <String> keys = (Enumeration<String>) properties.propertyNames();   
      while (keys.hasMoreElements()) {

 }
